name: The Queen's Dreams: A Glorious Savannah
description:
Hot and scorched.
Desolate and barren.
Sun high in a blazen sky.
Sand crystals sharp enough to tear skin.
Yet green, lush and fertile.
Rebirth.
Refresh.
A place mother nature blessed from a plentiful bosom.
A gracious offering to the Gods.
Blissful.
Peaceful.
Delightful and fair.
Blessed are all.
Blessed all whom care.
